## 8. Mapa de dependencias

### Store → Componentes

```
useCartStore.totalItems  →  NavBar.vue            ✅
useCartStore.*           →  CartView.vue           ✅
useCartStore.addItem     →  ProducQuickView.vue    ✅
```

### Composables → Componentes

```
usePricing    →  ProducQuickView.vue               ✅ adoptado
usePricing    →  CategorySection, ProductList,
                 ProductCard, HomeFeatured          ⏳ 4 copias de fmt() inline
useNewsletter →  Footer.vue, HomeNewletter.vue      ⏳ implementaciones locales
```

### API Service → Componentes

```
productosApi.getFeatured()  →  HomeFeatured.vue    ⚠️ directo, sin store
productosApi.getAll()       →  CatalogoView.vue    ✅
categoriasApi.getAll()      →  HomeView.vue        ⏳ datos hardcodeados
```

### Router — rutas con issues

| Ruta | Estado | Componentes afectados |
|------|--------|-----------------------|
| `/filosofia` | ⚠️ Redirige a home | NavBar, Footer, HomePhilosophy |
| `/contacto` | ⚠️ Redirige a home | NavBar, Footer |
| `/coleccion/fusion` | ❌ Sin ruta | HomeFusion CTA |
| `/terminos`, `/privacidad`, `/envios`, `/faq`, `/about` | ❌ Sin vista | Footer LEGAL/INFO |
| `/categoria/:slug` | ✅ Redirige a `/catalogo?categoria=` | Footer SHOP |

---

